{"type": "article", "id": 48022, "title": "这款轻质大容量背包，各种细节都为了更好收纳｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-07T23:11:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 39252, "name": "GAN"}, {"id": 46147, "name": "Thirty Third Parallel"}, {"id": 46148, "name": "Veiled"}, {"id": 46149, "name": "Moshi"}, {"id": 46150, "name": "Curious Chip"}, {"id": 22749, "name": "Héctor Serrano"}, {"id": 46151, "name": "Alex Sizemore"}, {"id": 46152, "name": "Hank Beyer"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 177, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171207191551XPEHsSjg0Wpl9McF.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #777777; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #777777} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Pip device by Curious Chip</h3><p>Pip 是一款基于 Raspberry Pi DIY电脑的一款趣味手持设备，目前正在 Kickstarter 网站众筹。这款产品的目标受众主要面向儿童、成年人、创客发明家以及教育行业从业者，你可以用 Pip 来创建和播放你自己的视频游戏，玩各种游戏，从 Snake 到 Pac-Man，再到 Minecraft。你也可以用 Pip 来钻研代码学习，学习如何制作属于自己的游戏。众筹价 50 英镑，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1464832835/pip-the-playful-handheld-device-you-program-yourse\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试预购</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191630eayFlpOBtGodUifH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712071916306FTg920jrl4oXLDi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712071916306reDK42l83pQythx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712071916315iIXxAGHPqNgjSfV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191631X47SIt8B3AlxqjHm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191631GgTj7yUucQzHMfK6.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539192\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Arcus laptop backpack by Moshi</h3><p>Arcus 多功能双肩包的设计灵感源自弧状云，如同云朵般轻量，同时具备大容量。它采用独特的弧形轮廓翻盖设计，拥有一个防冲击存物空间，可以收纳太阳镜、耳机等易碎物品。拉开 Arcus 的顶部翻盖，内部空间充裕，可以收纳外套、鞋、运动服、书籍以及更多其他物品。侧边拉链开口设计，便于拿取位于背包底部的物品。内设独立减震保护袋，为电脑等电子设备提供保护。</p><p>此外，Arcus 还配备了可调节胸带，有效缓解负重压力。背包侧边的弹性开口附袋可放置三脚架、伞或水瓶等物品，外出时方便拿取。背部还有两个安全隐蔽的拉链口袋，可贴身收纳贵重物品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191653ghoar4zHLxD58dQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191653gpMe8jTrinCs2wxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191653HuU75ba1Wqcsz4hL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191653XlT6sYfScrnZE8v2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191654SUXi0m9AtFyBMOgR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191654zOuMeBk8qFt60abN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The World's First Wooden Solar Charger by Veiled</h3><p>Veiled 公司经过两年研究与调查，在众筹平台 Kickstarter 上发布了世界首款木制便携太阳能充电器，由可降解的硬木材料制作而成，电池寿命长，快充 3.0 技术还能同时为两款手机充电。因其将木头作为原材料，使得电池可以始终保持适中温度，实现稳定而均匀地充电。此外，它能够在设备充满的情况下自动停止充电，保护 oPS 或 Android 设备电池充电过度受到损坏。这款充电器还能在人们断开设备连接的时候自动关闭。早鸟价 49 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/704939666/veiled-the-worlds-first-wooden-solar-charger?ref=cj57fp\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191725b84r75DzxgHkPdtq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657702\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191725PGbz4S3BDms8WwdO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712071917251hynJYO924BaEj5g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712071917255FElN2Ou7ArtKJd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Stark Collection of Furniture by Alex Sizemore and Hank Beyer</h3><p>这是设计师 Alex Sizemore 和 Hank Beyer 对一系列废弃材料进行再创造的探索结果。在俄亥俄州 Loraine，有一些世界上最均质且极具渗透性的砂岩层。2017 年夏天，他们花时间调查了当地家族采石场的运作情况。</p><p>据设计师了解，现在还没有已知的合成材料可以代替这些砂岩，他们将采石场那些切割下来的废弃材料重新想象，制成一个系列的桌子、凳子、托盘和灯，尤其是砂岩和灯光的组合，柔和的光线和坚硬的石头的对撞，很妙。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191755s7uHzRWgbrwIEj51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191755dRc7C2AlY5rMHyS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332955\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191756I6bGPAacUrYXzBWv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332955\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191755k308yZASLcTQer6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332955\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191756Wx5qgY6KUzZrQC2i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332955\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.core77.com/projects/70886/An-Exploration-of-Sandstone-and-Discarded-Materials-Resulting-in-a-Stark-Collection-of-Furniture\" rel=\"nofollow\">Core77</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>A Versatile Rechargeable Light for Home and Outdoors by Thirty Third Parallel</h3><p>美国达拉斯团队 Thirty Third Parallel 最近推出了一款可充电的模块化的多用途照明系统 PAL。它有模块化的 PAL 主灯头和多种配件组成，根据用途不同，配件也不同，其防水盒耐冲击性极强，完全可以抵御户外冒险中任何的恶劣环境。PAL 支持长达 15 个小时的稳定灯光使用。售价 89 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/973487661/pal-one-light-limitless-utility\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207192037D04m8IghaFq9YJlA.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017120719184343lgxtZNmnEy582a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191843OnL0mWQgRrtpe9kh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191843zU1O3bu8S7ZLsMFW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191843bRIMV6LqAGdDyNTB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191843pIxFkhmiBX7Pqyvb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.111765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>SAIL by Héctor Serrano for GAN</h3><p>GAN 是西班牙一个设计制造地毯、手织家具和饰品的时尚家居品牌。Sail 系列是其明星系列，意思是“风帆”，寓意永恒和简单。Sail 懒人沙发采用手纺纱棉毯的编织技术，由工匠手工制作而成，形成精致的菱形图案，既可休闲也能正式，不局限于特定场合。特别的是，其坐垫中心区域是故意暴露出来的接缝细节，用柔软的羊毛制成，灵感来自纸张褶皱，舒适且独一无二，售价 1050 欧元，<a href=\"https://shop.gan-rugs.com/es/espacio-sail/182-espacios-sail-puf-negro.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191914NfHoI3BLwWVRzM1t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.678385\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191914jlkJzI38LeC2Xrux.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665365\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712071919149NCumxqeltzvOfM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.394531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191914dCGg4pT9x1ctsRfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.446615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171207191914d1CSlU5suBHIwLNY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}